  "texts": [
    "In contrast, Llama3 70B demonstrates divergent trends: its spec-to-RTL performance improves from 40% to nearly 50% with more ICL examples, whereas its code completion performance declines from 40% to just above 30%.",
    "Llama3.1 70B achieves even better pass rates with ICL examples as compared to Llama3 for spec-to-RTL, and is fairly stable in code completion.",
    "RTL-Coder shows stability from 0-shot to 3-shot in both code completion and spec-to-RTL, only in very little improvements in the latter case.",
